              li.answer-box
                label
                  input(type='radio' name='question1' value='function')
                  span The design of public blockchains.
              li.answer-box
                label
                  input(type='radio' name='question1' value='global')
                  span The need for trusted third parties.
              li.answer-box
                label
                  input(type='radio' name='question1' value='number')
                  span The ability to send and receive transactions.

    

